				Spell level 56<BR>
Pet level is around 40 - always green.<BR>
Type is fire pet (wizard( - meaning it nukes and casts damage shield on itself.<BR>
It hits around 40 - quad hits.<BR>
HP around 2000.<BR>
<BR>
One interesting feature about this pet is its damage shield. All other pets you can equip with your own damage shield. Even other fire pets since they cast the wizzy damage shield which does around 12 damage. But on this one Casadeu of Flame doesn't stick (the 33 mage damage shield) - meaning this fellows damage shield must actually be the Casadeu of Flame.<BR>
<BR>
... a simple solo strategy would be to go against mobs with lots of attacks like monks and other melee types....<BR>
