				hey, i just wanted to add in that, i think us mages at higher lvls (ex. 30+) we should get snare/root/fear spells.  although our pets basically get root and snare(not snare really, just when the mob is running after you and your pet is wacking and taunting it) but not fear.  we should get a fear that is more resistable, as well as seperate snare/root series spells, i mean they should have a lesser duration time, and lesser casting time, heh, heck even more mana, these can be our &quot;feign death&quot; spells, you know our own get out of death free cards.  <BR>
