i mean all other classes get their own chances to get out of death.  in example, necromancer, monks, and shadow knights get feign death.  palys and clerics get divine aura.  druids and rangers get SoW (druids get evac).  shamans get SoW.  Wizards get shadow step as well as necros.  enchanters get rune spells and great stuns.  warrior has a chance of getting out with their high hp and high ac, also their berserking.  what do us mages get?  i mean that sounds like a stupid question because of this spell that i am posting on.  but WTH, why not ask anyways.  give us ONE of these excellent spells.  <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Thanks, <BR>
<BR>
Ulyessz Infernoblaze &lt;RunestorM&gt;<BR>
30th magician of the Mithaniel Marr server
